text: Lana Gorgadze (born 15 February 1997) is a Georgian footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Georgia women's national team. ==Career== Gorgadze has been capped for the Georgia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's footballers from Georgia (country) Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Georgia (country) women's international footballers Category:FC Martve players
